    "sections": {
      "A": "I with V/ii, then ii-V into IV (Ebmaj7) shifting to iv (Ebm) minor plagal, back to I, then II7 (C7) as V/V and ii-V turnaround ending on V (F7#5)",
      "A1": "Same as A but resolves: I, V/ii, ii-V to IV then iv, back to I, C7 (V/V), ii-V (Cm7-F7) landing on I",
      "B": "Descending sequence of ii-V-I units: C#m7-F#7-Bmaj7, Bm7-E7-Amaj7, Am7-D7-Gmaj7, then Gm7-C7 and Cm7-F7#5 leading back to home V",
      "A2": "Same as A1: I with secondary dominants, ii-V to IV/iv, C7 as V/V, ii-V resolving to I"
    },
    "modulates": false
  },
